Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.23,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:47.85,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的状况也能预知吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:48.89,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.66,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 这家伙的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.29,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想这样让我停车么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:03.35,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样蛮干可不像你啊 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.17,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.53,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.07,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 这是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.55,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.58,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 那可说不准
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:43.40,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照预知 同伴现在正赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.20,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:48.74,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是你们的同伴 2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.97,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.57,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋濑或
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:12.73,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟 所有人在那里不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.84,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.70,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有股有趣的气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:21.51,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在半路载上这家伙之后 去了趟鉴定科
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:24.73,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再根据警察的无线联络把他送到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.47,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉴定科？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.84,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.83,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到和第三具尸体的DNA一致的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.96,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.11,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉君 打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.45,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 这种东西都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.46,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:54.19,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放在我妻同学长大的那家养护设施里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.29,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:21:00.89,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 是我妻同学的脐带
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:02.99,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.07,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鉴定科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:10.33,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他们将脐带的DNA和第三具尸体比较了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:14.83,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其结果 二者的DNA完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.89,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎 不要听他的 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:21.46,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DNA是…一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:27.41,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 即二者基因相同 是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.05,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:31.83,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 不是的 不是的 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.87,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三具尸体的真面目是我妻由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.00,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的她已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:43.19,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 但是 由乃她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.23,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说结论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:48.70,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的那个她是假的我妻由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:52.36,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉君 快离开她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.32,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.90,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:01.62,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 雪 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:08.22,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不要 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:13.04,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…雪——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:49.96,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[数据传送]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,中,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.93,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.28,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:11.29,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:16.80,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you kill your friends, if you can fulfill your wish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.29,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you die for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.43,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:27.69,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life is a game It's a survival That's right! How do you start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:33.19,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time and Space It's a crossroad through a gate! Where do you go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:35.72,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.88,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need to live
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.85,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.13,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.03,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.04,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:55.91,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:56.42,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.07,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.12,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.27,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:13.87,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.93,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带刺的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.28,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你的故事里认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:11.29,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨之深皆因爱之切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:16.80,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会为一己之利置朋友于死地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.29,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会为了他人而牺牲自我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.43,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们又有何区别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:27.69,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！人生就是生存游戏　你要如何开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:33.19,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间和空间是分岔路口　你要往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:35.72,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻求永生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.88,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但生存的意义又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.85,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不知道世界的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.13,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是时空的乱入者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.03,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界不会因你而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.04,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则才决定着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:55.91,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我们凭着爱穿越古今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:56.42,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆发吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.07,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们浴火重生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.12,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.27,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奇迹之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:13.87,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是终结
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.01,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あとどれくらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:58.05,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高鳴る鼓動許される?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:09.35,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会いたくて涙 溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:14.95,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全ては未来を繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:22.57,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れる身体に絆感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:34.98,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度君を守ると誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.01,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟还要失去多少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:58.05,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这剧烈的心悸方能被宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:09.35,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要见到你 想到热泪盈眶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:14.95,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是连接着未来的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:22.57,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到崩坏身体的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:34.98,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意 再一次守护你 许下誓言
